I"Á<p>An easy way to visualize player tracking data with animation. Built using <a href="https://github.com/bokeh/bokeh">Bokeh Plots</a>, this tool can be used to visualise player movements for all sport. It also includes visualising voronoi and convex hulls, player speed and total distance covered by each player, interactively.</p>

<p>Link to tool: <a href="https://github.com/samirak93/Game-Animation">Game Animation</a></p>

